      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "Interesting\u2026 that was quicker than I expected.\n\nI see you\u2019ve
    started to understand how it responds. Not perfectly\u2026 but you\u2019re getting
    there.\n\nEvery action leaves a mark, every attempt shapes the outcome more than
    you realize.\n\nDon\u2019t rush it. Let things unfold naturally\u2026 observe,
    adjust, and try again.\n\nYou may not see the full picture yet\u2026 but trust
    me, you\u2019re on the right path.\n\nKeep going."
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: dc36b3fdc14f47ebb36fd484a67e268a, type: 2}
